comments: He\'s a pretty nice guy. Randomly dissapears during classes. He\'s very hard to catch outside of class. His lectures would be more interesting if he talks.
Alfonzo\'s class is pretty difficult, but he is a hunk! hubba, hubba, bau chicka-bow-wow! Love his class. Everyone enroll in his class next semester!.

A really nice guy, but his room was always messy for some reason. The class is not very hard if you do the reading and outdoor exercises. The exam was pretty easy. He\'s a pretty awesome guy and I dont mind staying after class.
He is a nice guy. He\'s also easy on the eyes. The class is difficult but he explains stuff well. I liked his class very much so, probabily the best in the department. Prof. Alfonzo rocks!
